{{Quote|The Imperial Games may seem like a goodwill event to foster harmony among diverse star systems, but they are in fact an exercise in Imperial propaganda, exploiting the prowess of honest sportsmen to serve an evil master.|A Rebel Alliance representative|<ref name="SWG:IGPC">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal|Rebel|Imperial Games Planning Center}}</ref>}}
The '''Imperial Games''' were a set of sports competitions held annually by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The Games for [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]] were set on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], but were cancelled when the planet was [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destroyed]]. They were a continuation of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic's]] [[Galactic Games/Legends|Galactic Games]]. The Games was administered by the [[Games Council|Imperial Games Council]].

